â¢ Two night-reading modes - for better reading comfort anytime;

â¢ Adjust the font style, font size, line spacing, and margin size;

â¢ Animation of turning pages;

â¢ Opportunity to crop margins â make the page look exactly the way you want.

Get fast file access and easy search!

â¢ All files are quickly found and instantly opened, even with built-in audio and video fragments;

